{"tid":744691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國球迷通宵慶祝 1人跳河慶祝身亡 至少2人在騷亂中遇難","createTime":"2018-07-16T06:39:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T17:52:12.000Z","uid":75969,"like":182,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"dc9e39f9338bcedc01acdc467165a0cd29c9800e","tid":744691,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:39:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180716/_2018071613220240959.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180716%2F_2018071613220240959.jpg&h=428cc957&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">法國人在凱旋門前狂歡慶祝。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n法國4-2擊敗克羅地亞，獲得2018年世界盃冠軍。法國多地有民眾通宵慶祝，但就在球迷們沉浸在歡樂中，一些極端球迷將狂歡演變成大騷亂。騷亂蔓延至馬賽、巴黎、安納西等多個城市。部分城市警方甚至需要動用了催淚彈。有些瘋狂的球迷直接爬上了救援車，這給警方的行動造成了很大的影響。英國媒體報道，已有兩名球迷在騷亂中遇難，還有一名男子因慶祝跳入運河身亡。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《每日郵報》報道，從巴黎北部的聖心大教堂，到左岸的索邦大學，「我們是冠軍」的喊聲震耳欲聾，響徹全城。狂歡者在凱旋門前燃放藍色、白色和紅色的煙火，警方不得不用發射水炮衝散人群。<br />\n<br />\n據法新社報道，有30餘人在當地時間晚上10點前打碎櫥窗玻璃，闖進巴黎香榭麗捨大道上的一間雜貨店，搶劫紅酒和香檳，隨後警方出動驅散人群。<br />\n<br />\n據報，在大街上，警察與鬧事者之間發生數次衝突，警察向人群施放催淚彈，鬧事者向警察投擲酒瓶、石塊，以及椅子等雜物回擊。在里昂有8人被捕；在馬賽有兩名警察受傷，10人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n在科西嘉島的阿雅克肖（Ajaccio），比賽結束時，法國和克羅地亞兩隊的支持者之間爆發小規模衝突，所幸無人受傷。在斯特拉斯堡和魯昂，當地年輕人與警察之間發生衝突，7名鬧事者被逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n另外，據英國媒體《衛報》及《鏡報》報道，已有兩名球迷在騷亂中遇難。<br />\n<br />\n據法國《世界報》報道，法國各地在慶祝世界盃奪冠時均有事故發生。在法國東部小鎮安納西（Annecy），<span style=\"color: red;\">一名逾50歲的男子在慶祝時頭朝下跳入運河中，由於河水過淺，該男子因頸部傷勢過重死亡。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180716/_2018071611592688270.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180716%2F_2018071611592688270.jpg&h=e2facdbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180716/_2018071611592639375.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180716%2F_2018071611592639375.jpg&h=f5c4d32a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/766885\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F766885&d=OBl%2FAhGcvaNzpESIBU6PjIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=bff93329\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F766885&h=5a9c845b\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/766885</a>"},{"pid":"2e209559f2e4c49043c7c899f22130c10732f2a6","tid":744691,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:41:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e4547487d273d7b1a2f837f77fabcd92d2a840","tid":744691,"uid":25858,"like":107,"dislike":1,"score":106,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:42:21.000Z","msg":"咁到可以騷亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808a5b395f511a250feec9cdbd526ea501c4a1e6","tid":744691,"uid":150400,"like":226,"dislike":2,"score":224,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:43:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7eed324610e67001fcdee5cea58cfd5b3ee23c04","tid":744691,"uid":194525,"like":127,"dislike":1,"score":126,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:43:15.000Z","msg":"癲過英格蘭班fan屎"},{"pid":"73f557955af1c75b561f22e818d44b4062752f90","tid":744691,"uid":111279,"like":118,"dislike":0,"score":118,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:43:39.000Z","msg":"究竟咁樣慶祝死嘅感覺係點?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e138030ae73a743c544b73f40e05850337dc9d","tid":744691,"uid":14918,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:44:02.000Z","msg":"c'est la vie"},{"pid":"8736c10454e0552315caff7e7e661af3055b9931","tid":744691,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:45:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\